descript.abstract: The parcel feature class contains a shape for every active Assessor Parcel Number (APN.) The parcel feature class is synchronized to the Alameda County secured tax roll on an annual basis in terms of Assessor Parcel Numbers.
descript.purpose: This layer contains stacked parcels in order to represent condo layers. This parcels layer created 12/2011

theme.themekt: REQUIRED: Reference to a formally registered thesaurus or a similar authoritative source of theme keywords.

idinfo.useconst: Warning: Adding up all GIS shape area column will overstate the total City of Berkeley land area since it contains 'stacked' parcels to represent condos. It is adviseable to use the Lot Square footage column for calculating total area.
idinfo.native: Microsoft Windows 2000 Version 5.2 (Build 3790) Service Pack 2; ESRI ArcCatalog 9.3.1.3000

altsys.altenc: Explicit elevation coordinate included with horizontal coordinates

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

attr.attrdefs: Land Management Module (FUND$); Alameda County Secured Tax Roll

attr.attrdef: Flag for Condos (Y=Yes, N=No, COM=Common Area)
Lot Square Footage - Total taxable parcel lot area. (Condo common area split amongst stacked condos)
Area of feature in internal units squared.

attrdomv.udom: Positive real numbers that are automatically generated.

cntorgp.cntorg: REQUIRED: The organization responsible for the metadata information.
cntorgp.cntper: REQUIRED: The person responsible for the metadata information.

cntaddr.addrtype: REQUIRED: The mailing and/or physical address for the organization or individual.
cntaddr.city: REQUIRED: The city of the address.
cntaddr.state: REQUIRED: The state or province of the address.
cntaddr.postal: REQUIRED: The ZIP or other postal code of the address.

cntinfo.cntvoice: REQUIRED: The telephone number by which individuals can speak to the organization or individual.
